##############################################################################
# ops-tensor Run Package Help
##############################################################################

NAME
    cann-ops-tensor - ops-tensor operator library run package

DESCRIPTION
    This package installs the ops-tensor operator library for CANN.
    The library provides tensor operation implementations for Ascend AI processors.

INSTALLATION
    To install this package, run:

        ./cann-ops-tensor-<version>-<os>-<arch>.run

    By default, files are installed to:
        Library:  /usr/local/Ascend/lib/libops_tensor.so
        Header:   /usr/local/Ascend/include/ops_tensor.h

OPTIONS
    --help          Show this help message
    --uninstall     Uninstall the package
    --noexec        Extract files without executing
    --target <dir>  Extract to specified directory

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
    TARGET_ENV      Installation directory (default: /usr/local/Ascend)

UNINSTALLATION
    To uninstall the package, run:

        ./cann-ops-tensor-<version>-<os>-<arch>.run --uninstall

    Or use the uninstall script directly:

        /usr/local/Ascend/share/info/ops_tensor/scripts/uninstall.sh

VERSION INFORMATION
    See version.info file in the package.

SUPPORT
    For issues and questions, please refer to the project documentation.
